talk1 = Array[String]([" Oh dear... it still hasn't been fixed!", "There was a cave-in a few weeks ago and the rubble's completely blocked up this old house.", "I've tried to get some Loox to help me but nobody cares about it.", "Nobody lives there any more, but I liked to draw the front of it...", "Oh well, it doesn't really matter."])
